#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:237
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Check this box to allow volume to be more than recommended value (sometimes "
"PulseAudio maximal volume exceeds the normal value). &kmix; restart is "
"needed for this setting to take effect."
msgstr ""
"Označite ovaj kvadratić da omogućite da glasnoča ima više predloženih "
"vrijednosti (ponekad PulseAudio maksimalna jačina prelazi normalnu "
"vrijednost). &kmix; potreban je restart da se primjene promjene."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:239
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Uncheck this item if there are audible sound distortions at the maximal "
